body: I ate these everyday for 10 days and I didnt see any difference in my milk supply sadly. But if it does work for some women, then they are great tasting at least!

author: Sarah Q.
title: Great option!
body: Yummy and live up to the hype and their purpose!

author: Joelys L.
title: Brownies!!
body: Yummy and very helpful. Thank you milky mama!!

author: Ashley M.
title: Tasted good but
body: I saw no increase in my supply. Even if it was just for a short period of time. But nothing happen. It was the reason for the purchase so I will not be getting them again because they didnt help me at all. However they did taste good

author: Sarah Q.
title: Great flavor!
body: Have used with my current breastfeeding journey as well as a previous one with good results and really do enjoy the flavor!

author: Briana W.
title: Brownie Amazing
body: This item made sure I produced enough milk to feed my 4 month old. I found myself always ready to feed.

author: paula h.
title: yummy
body: very tasty....I wanted ice cream with them

author: Daejenera B.
title: LOVE IT
body: Definitely helps my milk supply

author: Amber W.
title: Delicious brownies!
body: The emergency brownies work great in a pinch. When Im having an off day or if Ive been running errands and havent been able to hydrate or eat like needed I will eat an emergency brownie to help boost my milk supply for the day. They taste so good that its hard to only eat one!

author: Bri A.V.
title: Emergency brownies
body: Overall the brownies are the best lactation snack Ive ever had. The chocolate is a little rich but its perfect, my breasts filled up almost an hour after eating one. Im 6 weeks postpartum and prior to the brownies I pumped 4-5 ounces per now Im pumping almost 7 ounces per side two to three times per day

author: Fiumes N.
title: Just awesome ??
body: Im still using it

author: Alicia G.
title: They are okay
body: The flavor isn't terrible but not amazing but honestly the worst for me is that something, I'm not sure which ingredient, leaves little residue bits in your mouth. Sorry may not be explaining that well but basically unless I really really rinse out my mouth after eating them I have little bits in my mouth that I either feel on my tongue or feel my teeth biting down on. But I'm picky so might not bother everyone

author: Danae B.
title: No Title
body: I love these brownies. Great taste and they really have increased my milk supply. I couldnt be more pleased.

author: shelby e.
title: No Title
body: LOVED the emergency brownies! was using these plus pumping queen supplement and noticed my milk was getting more creamy and thick!

author: Hailey C.
title: Product didnt work for me
body: I was so excited to try. Love the company and what it sets out to do, but I took lady leche religiously for a month and at a box of brownies and never saw any increase in milk production. I was disappointed, but I understand every person responds differently.

author: Emily L.
title: Best mix out there.
body: Definitely the best drink mix I've come across.

author: Brittni F.
title: Just okay
body: Works good but I dont love the taste

author: Melani B.
title: Its the only treat that worked
body: I have tried a few products on my breastfeeding journey and none have worked except for these brownies. The proof came shortly after eating them. By the time you eat all twelve you should be back in the swing of things. I do recommend especially if you experience a dip in supply. I only gave it 4 stores because they are a little chalky. Full brownie flavor.

author: Fiendra F.
title: Delicious
body: I love these they're so good...

author: Stephanie W.
title: Was there a change?
body: So I've been getting these for a time now and they have helped increase my supply, but this last batch I got seems thinner and smaller than normal. These are expensive so I'm wondering if they will continue being like this or not.

author: Stephanie B.
title: The best
body: This product has really helped my breastfeeding journey this is my first time out of 4 children and I would definitely recommend. When I first started pumping I pumped 2oz now I pump more than 8oz my favorite out the sampler was the fruit punch and the oatmeal cookies but I have all the snacks with my coffee ?

productName: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Lactation Cookies
author: Katrina M.
title: Delicious
body: They were delicious. I think I ate more than I was supposed to but I couldn't help it they were so yummy.

author: Breanne R.
title: Lactation Lemoonade
body: Overall the taste was really good. The drink mix tasted like Minute Maid lemonade but did not help my milk production.

author: Sheena R.
title: Great product
body: I was at first skeptical of these brownies were going to work as i tried another brand and nothing. However, these were great. I noticed in about a day or two of eating the brownies that my supply was more. Also, when i ran out brownies, my production dipped a little so i knew it was because i hadnt eaten the brownies and i ordered more.

author: Reuben H.
title: Wife loves them
body: My wife really enjoys your products and says the brownies really help her maintain her supply for our baby. Thank you!

author: Afshan H.
title: LOVE!! A Must for Breastfeeding Mamas
body:
Absolutely delicious! Immediately helped my milk supply increase and baby has more creamy milk. I eat one daily! So thankful I found Milky Mama, I feel more confident breastfeeding my baby.
I tried so many other brands of supplements, either baby didnt tolerate the ingredients, tasted horrible, or didnt work.

Now, I always keep a supply of the Milky Mama lactation and emergency brownies in my pantry.

Thank you Milky Mama!

author: Hailey V.
title: Great!
body: The cookies were good! Recommended to eat 1-2 a day so maybe a bigger box or bigger cookies would be awesome

author: Aliah A.
title: Unfortunately didnt work
body:
I was looking forward to receiving the emergency brownies in hopes that it would help. I was surprised to see the opposite, I actually had less breast milk the days I ate the brownies. I had to double check on the site and the box to see if by mistake I purchased brownies to help reduce milk when you stop breastfeeding, but no they promote increase of breast milk.
I started to gain weight so I ended up throwing them out.
Very expensive also, plus shipping, and long wait to receive them. I wont purchase them again.

author: Stephanie C.
title: We will see
body: I ordered these when I noticed my supply taking a huge dip and havent noticed too much of a difference. I wanted to give them another shot so I ordered some more brownies, drops, and oatmeal cookies so we will see. They actually dont taste bad my only complaint is that they are a little to sweet for my taste.

author: Bianca S.
title: These work!
body: I didnt know what to think because these brownies are so delicious! But after just one week my milk supply doubled I went from nursing baby full time and pumping 5-6 oz a day to 9-10 oz a day.

author: Mecheliz S.A.
title: LOVE IT!
body: Perfect gift for a new mama!

productName: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Lactation Cookies
author: Carley B.
title: Worth every penny!
body:
I got the peanut butter chocolate chip, emergency brownies, milky melon and and pumpin punch and it all were so good!!!
Unfortunately my body wont produce anymore. As much as I wanted to I know it happens.
I highly recommend this product and company to all the new mommas!

author: Emily L.
title: Great lactation cookie.
body: Taste we as amazing and much better than any been other cookies I've tried.

author: Mimi H.
title: Emergency brownie
body: Great product ! Definitely notice an increase in my supply! Didnt need to pump I collected over 4 ounces of milk from just my collector cups

author: Michelle M.V.
title: It really works!
body: This product has become a staple in my pumping routine. My little one isnt a strong nurser so I have to pump after each feeding to provide supplement bottles. Since I have started using this my volume has increased significantly taking the stress off of making sure I have supplemental bottles. Thanks!!

author: Priyanka A.
title: Not much difference
body: I havent notice much milk production because of that Im going to order another pack and then well update you

author: Natalie B.
title: Emergency Brownies
body: They are AMAZING. Taste great, work well and are the perfect snack. They have saved my supply on more than one occasion.

author: Courtney L.
title: Really works!
body: These are so yummy!! And they really work. After eating one brownie I could tell a difference in a matter of a day!

author: Taylor S.
title: Pretty good!
body: I've been a customer since 2015 the first time I got these they worked awesome for me and this time around they were not a disappointment. My milk was fattier and while it didn't help my supply increase it was able to keep it stable as I was having to take steroids. Super thankful for this product

author: Alejandra P.D.
title: These are my life savers
body: When I had my baby I'd see these ads online and I always thought that these kinds of things were not real, until a friend of my sister's recommended these to me and I tried them. I was almost immediately proven wrong and I was happy about. Now, whenever I'm in a pinch, and my supply drops because I have been so tired and had to drop my middle of the night pumping sessions so I can sleep a little, these are my go-to. They work. I'm so thankful for Milky Mama and for my sister's friend who recommended them to me.

author: candie h.
title: love the brownies
body: they worked wish it did take so long to get them buy the time i got them and they started to work i figured out i should have order the day i got them in order to be able to have one every day so now down to using them two day and then wanting two days that way i can use them longer as it cost 20 for a box and then 12 in shipping thats 32 for not even two weeks

author: Autumn W.
title: Can't live without
body: Definitely saw an increase in milk and milk quality, my milk was more creamy and fatty. Definitely have a glass of milk with it

author: Kia G.
title: Brownies
body: I did not notice a big difference in mild production with these brownies however, I suppose they possibly helped me maintain my supply since I began my period when I began to eat them. They are good, but I prefer other products that they sell for milk production compared to this one.

author: Shakeria M.
title: Milky melon
body: The drink mix for the melon drink was pretty good. I like the lemonade mix as well. I had that from a previous purchase.

author: Robyn D.
title: On point
body: They worked immediately!

author: Karrie B.

body: Im four weeks pp. I tried these with my first baby and I noticed a big increase with my supply. Now, with my second, these brownies are keeping my supply up 24/7. I dont pump. I feed every two hours, sometimes every hour.

author: Bridget S.

body: These brownies taste like regular, delicious, fudgy brownies! My husband even tasted it and was so jealous! And they work, too!!

author: Bri-yanna B.

author: Sierra M.
title: Amazing!
body: I love it. It does exactly what I need it to. I have no problem keeping up with my daughter's milk needs!

author: Ashley K.

body: I love the emergency brownies as they have been helping me produce more breastmilk for my little one; as my milk production has been struggling.

body: I ordered these after spending a day away from my baby for the first time in 3 months. Going back to work. My supply quickly dropped. I ordered these and they came quickly. After a couple days my supply went back up and baby stopped fussing from the lack of supply.

author: Alex I.
title: Brownies were great - wish shipping were free
body: They were great. Tasty. Not sure if it did anything regarding milk, Im pretty low regardless.

author: Brittney H.
title: Love them
body: I absolutely love the brownies. They taste great and help me produce like crazy. I stopped eating them for a while and saw the decline in my production. I am ready to order my next couple of boxes.

body: It was great thank you

title: Emergency Brownies and drink
body: I've had emergency brownies before and this time I felt they were hard and dry. Before they were moist and chocolate-y. This time I wondered if they were old. Not pleasant at all this time around.

author: DVonia O.
title: Tasty & Effective
body: These tasted sooo good and definitely helped with my supply. I went from pumping 1-2 oz to getting 3-4 oz after eating these for only a couple of days. If I werent limited to 2 a day, Im sure I wouldve finished the box a lot sooner

author: Bri-yanna B.
title: My favorite!
body: My absolute favorite of the drink mixes! The taste is like true fruit punch with just enough sweetness. Absolutely refreshing and delicious, but also helped significantly increase my milk production. I wasnt filling up fast enough after feedings but with these I feel almost engorged after 2 hours.

author: Kasandra
title: Ingredients
body: I wish I wouldve read the ingredients before purchasing. My mistake. Id rather eat my sugar than drink it. I tried 1 packet and it was good but I couldnt get over the fact of how much sugar it had. Not sure if it actually does help supply because I couldnt get myself to drink any more.

author: Mecheliz S.A.
title: Delicious
body:
Delicious. Perfect snack.
Not sure if there is any difference from regular brownies vs emergency ones.

author: Heidi G.
title: Brownies
body: The brownies tasted great, unfortunately for me they didnt help boost my supply. I had a great supply for about 2 1/2 months postpartum and then around that time I got my period back. After that my supply continued to deplete. I do feel that the milky mama products slowed the progression of my decreasing milk supply, but didnt bring it back to where I originally started. I know these products work really well for people, but regretfully not me.

author: Brooklyn T.
title: No change in supply

author: Ashley K.

author: Brittni F.
title: Ehh

author: Dreena C.
title: Great Products

author: channa b.
title: taste good but go bad quick

author: Mimi H.
title: Lactation brownies

author: PAIGE S.
title: The Best
body: I notice a difference when I take the drops within a couple hours and its drastic. Love this product!

author: Carol M.
title: Best ever
body: Love the flavor. I was going to give up but this worked! I saw the difference after the first pack.

author: Suillen O.
title: Heaven sent cookies
body: The oatmeal chocolate chip cookies are not only amazing at helping me produce milk but they are absolutely delicious. I have struggled producing breast milk with my first 3 kids. With my newest bundle of joy I started eating these cookies a week before having my baby and now have been able to pump and nurse him for 4 amazing months. I am forever grateful!

author: Brittni F.
title: Worth it!
body: These work great

author: Kristin M.
title: My 2nd time using
body: This will be my 2nd time using this product with a 2nd child and I started using them this time sooner and regularly then the 1st time and for the 1st time EVER Ive been able to pump along with EBF and build up a freezer stash. I am so beyond thrilled with this product. Ive been EBF for 7 years total with 3 babies back to back and I wish I had found out about these sooner. My milk is more creamy and fatty than its ever been with my other 2 babies. Shipping was fast and the brownies were soft and delicious. I usually have a couple days between batches and I miss them when I dont have them lol a great treat!

author: Yolanda V.
title: Emergency brownies
body: Emergency brownies taste Delicious

author: Hala H.
title: Great Taste But Long Wait ??
body: These brownies taste insanely good! I definitely plan to invest more in these. However, they DO take a long time to ship and receive. Took about 2 weeks.

author: Kaylin M.
title: Thank you!
body: First of all, these brownies are SO good. They are rich and best enjoyed with your favorite kind of milk! I ordered 3 packs and put the 2 I wasn't using in my chest freezer where they have stayed tasty. Secondly (and most importantly), they helped increase my milk production! I was producing about 1 oz extra/ day with multiple pumping sessions and now produce 4-6 oz extra/ day. This has helped my freezer stash SO much! Thank you Milky Mama!!!

author: Ashia W.
title: Great product
body: The product is great but the shipping and receiving of the product is very slow and annoying and they don't do anything for good customers that order all the time. And they just have the same answer for Amy complaint

They were all frozen immediately upon delivery and I would pull them out as I ate them over the course of 3-4 weeks. So I expected them to all taste the same. Seemed like the brownies in each box were from multiple batches. You would think one box would be the same batch. I was also sad the expedited shipping was $25 my first order then it was raised to $35 on my following orders.

title: The Drought is Over!
body: I literally felt like my boobs were drying out and starting feeling discouraged. I started to only pump an ounce here and 3 ounces here and could barely keep up with my sons feedings. I called a lactation consultant and she told me to try a dietary supplement, Moringa . When I looked at the ingredients in Pumping Queen, I knew that I had to give it a try. I started making milk again immediately and stashing milk again. My Willow pump is running over with milk on my right boob. I have to stop it, empty it out, and continue pumping. Milk appears to be creamier and has more fat. I love it here! I recommend this product 100%! RUN and put this in cart and checkout immediately. It takes a while to ship but well worth it! Thanks Milky Mama!

author: Colleen S.
title: Mmmm, good
body: Before Milky Mama, I was pumping 2-3 oz and tried power pumping, but my milk supply did not increase. I tried lactation cookies at my local store, nada. I came upon Milky Mama during my second month post-delivery and ordered cookies, brownies, and a smoothie mix. During my first week of use, I noticed my milk supply gradually increase with use. I, now, pump 4-6 oz each pump, which is 7-8x a day and in between pumping. I can feel fullness compared to before and it has helped me build my milk stash. I prefer the cookies and the brownies; however, I have only tried oatmeal, peanut butter chocolate chip, and oatmeal chocolate chip. I chose these 3 based on sugar contentsince I dont consume a lot of sugar, daily, these taste great for me. I have been using Milky Mama products for the past 2 1/2 months and I am hooked. If youre on the fence to give these products a try, I would recommend buying at least a months supply to determine whether theyre for you or not. I hope this review helps.

title: My Favorite!
body:
Its been over a week since Ive purchased products from MilkyMama & let me just saythese are my FAVORITE. They taste like butter crunch cookies and i just have to stop myself from eating so many.

As far as how the products works, they do an amazing job but i think you have to know what to eat with what. All of these snacks are great for breastfeeding mommies but i feel like these with the oatmeal chocolate chip and the lemooonade mix works great together. I went from pumping less than 2oz a session to now 4-5oz a session. When I breastfeed my baby, i have to pump after because sometimes its still leaking.
So two cookies & lemoonade mix a day will allow you to produce more than enough for your baby.
Ill be making more purchases & I am so grateful that i found this company!

I be woken up with my breasts full these last two days for the first time in two months. Thank you for this great product ! And they taste great!

author: Afshan
title: Miracle Brownies
body:
I recently had the flu and took medication that dropped my milk supply significantly. I exclusively breastfeed so it was extremely stressful for baby and myself. I bought the emergency and lactation brownies immediately after reading all the positive reviews. I love that they are fenugreek free since this gives my baby gas and colic. I was worried my baby would not tolerate the Milky Mama ingredients but he was fine! Immediately after eating half an emergency brownie - my supply started to increase. While I breastfeed and pump, the supply has improved significantly. The milk is definitely more fatty which satisfies my baby. I eat the lactation brownies daily and sometimes the emergency ones when I need a boost.
The taste is so delicious OMG. Most lactation treats on the market taste terrible and dont work!
Milky Mama works and tastes great! I feel more confident and happy breastfeeding now. :)

If you breastfeed, keep a stash of these in the freezer. If you suddenly get sick or need these urgently, it takes about 10-13 days to receive them which is too long for emergencies.

title: Taste incredible and they work!!
body:
These cookies are divine! I have definitely noticed an increase in my supply. I tried these and the emergency brownies and I went from the pediatrician asking us to supplement with formula at every feeding to EBF and pumping an extra 3-4 oz every morning. Ive already ordered more and some other flavors too!
My only recommendation is dont wait a full two weeks to pop some in the freezer. I noticed after about 10 days they didnt taste quite as fresh (still good though!) but then when I thawed one that I had frozen after just a few days, it tasted just like when they first arrived. By two full weeks after arrival they were fairly dry tasting. Now Ill just pop all my treats in the freezer when I get them and take them out a couple at a time to preserve the quality!

author: Allison L.
title: Getting Through the Weekend
body: The lemoonade was a good way to keep things rolling through the weekend for me. I dont generally pump on weekends when Im with my baby, but didnt want my supply to drop by Monday. So, I drank one glass of lemoonade each day. My supply stayed up just fine! I dont give 5-stars for 2 reasons. One, this doesnt taste like Country Time, Dont get me wrong, it tastes better than some of the herbal lactation teas I have tried, but there is still something a bit off about the flavor. Two, I agree with other reviewers that its less than convenient to have two servings per pouch. I dumped the contents into a dish and discovered that one serving is equal to about 1TBSP of powder, but 1 serving pouches would be much more convenient to handle.

author: Allison L.
title: Game-Changer!
body: I admit, I was skeptical, but this was a game-changer for me! I was struggling and sometimes failing to produce 18 oz. of milk per day for my hungry munchkin while working full time. I was trying all the tricks I used with my first baby (herbal lactation teas, oatmeal every day for breakfast), but it just wasnt helping enough. Enter the Milk Goddess tincture. It took effect right away, and my first day I pumped 4 oz. above what I needed. Over the first week, I banked 17 oz. in the freezer beyond what my baby ate. Thats almost an extra days supply! Now I am producing enough that I can have no worries if my baby goes up to 21 oz. a day like his big brother did.

author: Randi
title: Tastes okay, but it works!
body:
I have struggled with latching, pumping and production from day 1. I have done it all! The snacks (homemade and purchased), recommended drinks, massage, cluster feeds, lactation consultants, heat pads, cooling pads, cracked/busted nipples, all of it. Ive been supplementing with formula since the first week of my daughters life. Suddenly, my production dropped to nothing. I went from pumping 4oz every 3-4 hours, to pumping 4oz all day. I immediately ordered emergency brownies and lady leche supplement. It didnt work immediately, but by day 3 I had felt a difference in how fast my breasts refilled, how much I was producing, and thicker consistency. By a week (today 11/18), my production was back to normal! Ive been pumping at least 3.5oz every 3 hours. Were working on breastfeeding again, and Im noticing my let down has improved also. Overall, very happy with my purchase. It was worth the investment!

Also, it tastes like grape as described. But sort of like the cough syrup grape. Not great but its not bad.

title: Love !
body: I had twins in September and couldnt produce enough for both boys so I had to supplement with formula . I was only pumping up to 2oz combined with both breast only getting 3 bags a day . Now Im getting 3oz and some times 4oz up to 4 bags a day . Ive also had pumps up to 5-7oz at a time here and there . I just placed a second order and cant wait for them to arrive !

author: Randi
title: THEY WORK & theyre yummy!
body: I have struggled with latching, pumping and production from day 1. I have done it all! The snacks (homemade and purchased), recommended drinks, massage, cluster feeds, lactation consultants, heat pads, cooling pads, cracked/busted nipples, all of it. Ive been supplementing with formula since the first week of my daughters life. Suddenly, my production dropped to nothing. I went from pumping 4oz every 3-4 hours, to pumping 4oz all day. I immediately ordered emergency brownies and lady leche supplement. It didnt work immediately, but by day 3 I had felt a difference in how fast my breasts refilled, how much I was producing, and thicker consistency. By a week (today 11/18), my production was back to normal! Ive been pumping at least 3.5oz every 3 hours. Were working on breastfeeding again, and Im noticing my let down has improved also. Overall, very happy with my purchase. It was worth the investment!

Its taken so much stress off of me to produce enough and Im going to be ordering the emergency brownies to keep on hand for the next growth spurt.

author: Audrey C.
title: Taste great!
body: I started these just as I was tapering off of a lactation medication so I cant be 100% sure, BUT since starting these I've seen a huge increase in my milk output!! I went from struggling to make1.5-2 oz to making 3-4 oz with ease every pump. Thats a big deal for me being that my girl drinks about 5-5.5 oz of breast milk now at almost 4 months old (IUGR baby). I stopped the meds after today & I've ordered another box bc its going to be that time of the month (2nd one post partum) & my milk might dip again. These brownies seemed to help a lot during my first post partum period. I'm hoping this time around the brownies will work its magic again! This could be a staple for me if it works out again & they taste like that molten chocolate lava cake

Not too sweet, the right amount of caramel/salt and oatmeal. I love these so much that everyone wants to try them! Im adding these to my auto ship with my Pumpin Punch and Milky Melon drink mixes! I also use Lady Leche and Dairy Duchess supplement drops and have seen an increase in my supply and my milk is creamier after 1 week! Thank you Milky Mama!!!!

Im now back up to 4-6oz per pump now. I love this stuff and it has definitely helped me tremendously!

title: Very Amazing!
body: I was struggling to produce, mostly because I had an electric plug in pump with 4 kids and no time to sit around in one spot. Between getting no sleep with a newborn and 1 yr old then not having time to pump it was thee worst feeling ever not be able to feed my baby the way I wanted too. Now with these wonderful products you offer and a wireless pump I'm able to give my baby all the nutrients she need. I would not be able to get this much milk without the emergency brownies and Lady Leche liquid. Thank you so much for these products they truly work especially for struggling moms.

author: Madeline O.
title: Miracle Supplement!
body: I swear by this supplement for increased milk production! I am exclusively pumping and was producing 90-120ml per session which was at the cusp of what my baby consumes each feeding (he eats 120ml). I was stressed about having to supplement with formula when I couldnt pump enough to feed my baby, so I looked into non-fenugreek supplements. After taking this supplement once daily (2 dropper fulls) I am pumping 120ml at a minimum and typically more like 160-190ml each session. Im yielding so much milk that I actually dropped my 1 hour power pumping session each day and havent experienced a decrease in milk output. One other positive of this supplement is it has a lot more servings than many of the pills out there so I feel like Im getting more bang for my buck. I cant recommend this product enough!

He eats fine when I feed him directly with my breast he gets what he needs. So I wanted to try these drops to increase my supply. I started doing the drops once a day. Then when I did not see a change in my supply, I did them twice a day. I put the drops in my drink. I have been doing them twice a day and still do not see a change. I'm giving this product three stars because I love what this company does and I see other moms have great results. My body just doesn't work that well I guess. I might try the brownie treats. I hope other moms continue to buy this product if it helps them though!

title: Obsessed
body: Ive been using Milky Mama for about a month or 2 and Im hooked! The products are very tasty and they actually do work. I can tell my milk has increased and is creamier than before . My Baby stays full for a longer time so I think it has helped there also.

author: Samantha s.
title: IT WORKS !
body: Best thing Ive bought to help my milk supply. When my was home it was hard to find time to pump so my milk supply dropped these brownies help me so much and they taste soooo good taste like a regular brownie.

author: Ela T.
title: It worked!
body: I was down to 2 oz per session. I was desperate as my LO did NOT like formula. I am now on average 4 oz per pumping session and 10oz during my power pump. Im so grateful!!!

author: Carrie C.
title: Must try
body: Amazing!! Must try!

author: Lindsey A.
title: Very Helpful & delicious!
body: I am thrilled to have these brownies in my breast milk support arsenal! They are so convenient, they taste great, and I do believe that they help to support my milk supply.

author: Carrie C.
title: If youre not sure, TRY IT
body: At first I was a little skeptical. Ive heard good things, but have tried so many things and figured I give this a try. I originally was purchasing to try the different variety of drink mixes for a longer period of time. Im one of those people who need to try something for a week to see if it was effective. I ended up LOVING EVERYTHING IN THIS SAMPLE PACK! The cookies were so yummy and I started making more smoothies because of this!

author: claire b.
title: Love it!
body: I havent noticed a huge increase in amount (Im already a pretty good producer) but I have noticed that my milk looks so much richer and baby seems far less gassy after eating. Highly recommend!

author: Justice C.
title: No change
body: This product hasn't affected my breast milk in anyway. I've still been pumping a lot less then 0.5oz.

author: claire b.
title: Great!
body: Delicious and will perk up my supply especially if I missed a pump or two.

author: claire b.
title: Love it!
body: Delicious!

author: Tracey L.
title: Increase in milk supply right away!
body: As soon as I started eating the emergency brownies, I saw my milk supply increase! I was getting about 7oz combined pumping and it increased to 11oz combined after the first day!

author: Carrie C.
title: Great! But the flavor wasnt how I thought-still good though
body: This is good! I just thought the flavor more closely resembled lemon grass. I still enjoyed the taste of it. I did notice my supply increase on day 3! Definitely worth the purchase! Because each packet is 2 portion sizes, I would just use my one water bottle, fill it with 20 oz and dump the whole packet, drinking the 1/2 the lemonade in one sitting.

author: Carrie C.
title: Amazing!!
body:
Loved the taste of this! By far my favorite flavor. I noticed an increase in my supply on day 3. Plan on purchasing this again! I break each packet into 1 bottle and drink 1/2 in the morning and in the early afternoon.

It made a difference. Cheers to my second 1/2 tonight (:

author: Chauntel P.
title: Emergency Brownies
body: I Started the emergency brownies on Monday and my milk has increased tremendously! I actually had to stop pumping before I started taking the emergency brownies because I wasnt producing enough milk for my babygirl. Now that I started the brownies I can pump while feeding my baby! My boobs also leak nonstop in the morning. Im able to pump 8 oz apon waking and later on throughout the day I can pump 5.6 oz. I used to be able to only pump 2 oz out of each breast! Thank you milk mama !

author: Mia
title: Good
body: Super chocolatey and sweet. Didnt really notice an increase in milk production though

author: Brenda A.
title: Didnt work
body: Tasty but didnt see a difference after 2 orders

author: Mia
title: Good
body: They taste really good but I didnt notice any major results

author: Katie
title: Didn't see much of an increase at all
body: Bought these emergency brownies in hopes that they would be a miracle product to boost my supply as I've been underproducing since about 4 months postpartum, likely because I'm an exclusive pumper getting regular periods. Unfortunately, they didn't work for me. My supply has only increased by 3 ounces a day on a good day; I saw much better results drinking Mother's Milk tea and doing a power pump. Giving three stars because I do think they helped a little, and the taste is actually pretty good.

author: Lisa B.
title: Lady Leche with Emergency Brownies
body: I was only producing 2-3 ounces per pump while taking fenugreek supplement and eating munchkin milkmakers cookies. I switched to using the lady leche with one emergency brownie per day and within 3-4 days my supply increased to 3-5oz per pump. Still 3-5oz a week in, but I have been able to stash some supply. Hoping it would increase a little more, but even what it did increase, I feel it was worth it.

author: Tala S.
title: Right away
body: I had originally just ordered to try to increase my supply but within the first two I saw such a change in the consistency of my milk, it used to be so watery and now it is full of all the good fats my little baby needs! It did increase my milk output by few ounces a day!

author: Bertha C.
title: Emergency Brownies
body: I feel like theee years ago these were bigger in size. I dont know I know in the past they have worked Im not to sure it had the same affect this time around.

author: Britney W.
title: Taste good but didnt work
body: I love been taking the Lady Leche and the emergency brownies twice daily for two weeks and my milk supply has not changed. The brownies taste great but unfortunately they didnt work for me.

author: kiara r.
title: Delicious!
body: These taste amazing! They taste like fresh baked brownies!

productName: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Lactation Cookies
author: Kiara R.
title: Works
body: Works and are really good!

author: Erika C.
title: Love it
body: It was good, the taste its good.

author: kiara r.
title: Amazing!
body: Out of all the lactation supplements Ive tried, Milky Momma is the only one that helps and tasted good! The flavor is fantastic. It doesnt taste like most lactation drinks. Its was like I was really drinking a lemonade.

author: Kiara R.
title: Takes time to work
body: Only eat one or you are going to be engorged. Doesnt work for about an hour or so!

author: nikki O.
body: Tastes amazing, super light within a few hours my nipples were leaking! Very happy

author: Kiara R.
title: Makes milk creamier
body: Doesnt taste like grape, more tea taste than anything!

author: Kiara R.
title: Works but takes a minute
body: Overall the product is amazing!!! The oatmeal chocolate chip cookies are good but Im not a fudgey person so the brownies were ok. I also need up ordering the salted caramel cookies and peanut butter chocolate chip cookies and they were both my favorite! When it comes to the drink mixes some were good and some I could do without. The strawberry lemonade was my favorite. Overall, the products work but dont expect them to work within three days to a week. I didnt notice a difference in my supply until two and a half weeks in. It wasnt a tremendous amount of difference but my slacker boob aka my left boob makes 3-4 ounces each pump versus 2 ounces that it would produce before and in my good boob Im getting 8-13 ounces out versus 6-8 ounces before. Consistency and being hydrated is key!!!!

author: Candace F.
title: Lady Leche
body: It has been going good!

author: Karelin R.
title: Didnt work this time around
body: I ordered more emergency brownies as a just in case since they worked so well for me the first time around. I got covid and being sick dried me up. So I started eating the emergency brownies and its not doing anything for me this time around ?

author: Amanda C.
title: No Title
body: These work well.. I have had them before.ni and always struggled with milk supply and wanting to know my baby was getting plenty. These boost and also give some energy. They are delicious.. I would highly recommend.

author: Sara P.
title: Really work
body: I was skeptical and I thought if they dont work its a good excuse to eat brownies. But they really work. Dont expect a miracle though. I usually get an oz pumping after feeding my baby, now I get 2. But that is double what I was getting and my freezer is building because of that.

author: nikki O.
body:
Lady Leche is amazing and works very quickly. I woke up in the middle of the night leaking. SO happy!
The flavor is super yummy

author: nikki O.
body: First offThe taste is absolutely AMAZING! Secondly, This product truly works wonders & does NOT upset my babies tummy.

author: jessica a.
title: Brownies
body: Honestly I was excited about trying these because its very important for me to get my supply back up until my baby is at least 1 but the brownies were very dry and didnt taste the best but of course I know they will not taste like regular brownies but they were very dry and hard for me to eat.

author: Dezare L.
title: Oh they work!
body: I ordered the emergency brownies because my supply seemed like it was on the low side and I wanted to continue pumping between feeds since Im going back to work soon. I went from pumping 2.5-3oz to 5oz and thats without completely emptying out.

author: Shannon F.
title: Milky Mama
body: I love the taste of the cookies. They did help produce more milk and love the watermelon juice.

author: Amber B.
title: Love it
body: I was nervous about how this would taste but it tasted good and dissolved almost instantly under my tongue. My milk production has seemed better and my milk has seemed better quality sense using this product along with the brownies.

author: Jecelin M.
title: Miracle Brownies
body: I love these brownies . I just had me second child after ten years & with such an age gap there are alot of things that are new to me. With my second child I have struggled with latching causing me to stress and a decrease in my milk supply very early on . I was skeptical about these brownies but after the 6 day I did notice a difference in the amount I pumped and the consistency . Now I want to make these products part of my everyday diet along with teas and pumping to maintain my supply . Its also a plus that the brownies taste great ! Thank you Milky Mama

author: Kirbie B.
title: They really work!
body: I love these brownies!! I warm them in microwave for 20 seconds and they taste so good!! They really do work! I went from pumping 1 bag a day to pumping 4-5 bags a day!

author: Janelle D.
title: Love it
body: It's been helpful. I no longer worry if I'm making enough because the milk in storing in the freezer is enough for baby to go visit grandparents and not have to have any formala she wouldn't drink wasted

author: Cierra L.
title: A first time breastfeeding mama..
body: After doing tons and tons of research trying to find the best product out there to help with my breastfeeding struggles as a first time breastfeeding mama, everything kept leading me back to Milky Mama! I took the free quiz and ended up ordering the Lady Leche.. it came in very quickly and I immediately began consuming the product, as directed. I am now 8 days into using the product & I can tell a MAJOR difference.. I noticed a difference after 2 days.. My milk is way more creamier, my refill is more consistent, my letdown has improved and become more frequent during/before feedings. I am overall very very VERY happy with my order. I will be ordering another bottle asap along with some other goodies. Thank you Milky Mama for helping ease my worries and giving me a peace of mind while I tackle this journey with my little one.

author: Vanessa S.
title: Best brownies ever!
body: I love the emergency brownies, they have given me about 10-15oz more per day!!!

author: Summer W.
title: Wonderful!
body: Unexpectedly, I started my cycle while still breastfeeding and I could tell my supply took a plunge. These came in so quickly after I ordered and they have worked like a dream! They actually taste good, too. My supply is back to normal and I don't have to supplement for the time being. I am keeping these on standby in my freezer in case it happens again. Thank goodness for these brownies!

author: Sara L.
title: Had High Hopes..
body: Unfortunately this product did nothing for me. The brownies do taste good but my supply did not change. I thought Id give these a try since I was dealing with stress due to starting up work and my supply was lessening. I was really hoping they worked!

author: Juliua M.
title: Helpful
body: Good !

author: Nicole
body: Im amazed with how well this product works! I dont exaggerate when I say within 24 hours your milk supply will increase. And if doesnt hurt my babies tummy.

author: Kirbie B.
title: Life saver!
body: This has been a life saver for me! I was getting so stressed out about not producing a lot of milk which was only making it worse. So I decided to try Lady Leche along with both Emergency brownies and also purchased lactation brownies. Within a week I started noticing a difference! I went from 1 bag a day in the fridge to now currently have 10 bags in fridge!! Getting ready to start freezing it! I eat a brownie and Lady Leche every morning Super happy with results and brownies taste so good!

author: Jamie R.
title: Amazed
body: Took about 24 hours or so but definitely more milk and did look a little more creamy definitely something I'll be buying again

author: Janelle D.
title: I should have ordered earlier ??
body: They arrived within the delivery dates I was given. They're delicious and the packaging is so custom I love it. It's nice to have a dessert treat that my children and husband won't get into. It's been almost a decade since my last breastfeeding adventure. I wish I'd had these then. I'm not a very big person and didn't gain much weight during the pregnancy. I was worried about being able to make enough milk for my baby and not having to supplement like I did with my son. He was a much bigger baby than the one I have now. Until the milky mama products I've been making enough to keep her content and nothing left to store for her to be able to go to grandmas for an afternoon , baby absolutely will not take formula. After the milky mama I now have enough to feed and store so she can go visit and I can do things with my other kids away from the house. Or they can help me with her and I get other things done and get back to her with no guilt about what she ate or didn't eat. Thank you. I'm already waiting for my next order.

body: I am a huge fan of the lactation supplements, they have helped my supply soo much. Enriching my milk, giving me a more to feed and filling much faster. The flavors fantastic, and easy to take.

title: They did not work for me :(
body:
I bought this item to help with my milk production. After getting my period back I went from producing naturally 5-6oz every three hours to 2 oz every three hours.
I bought this out of desperation to help me so I could keep breastfeeding. I think my body is not wanting me to. So long story short this product might be fantastic but it did not work for me.

title: Awesome!
body: I got these brownies because I love chocolate and needed a decent and quick boost in my supply for various reasons. Not only did it boost my supply like I wanted but I got to be in chocolate bliss as I did it. Double win! Definitely will buy again.

author: Lamia C.

body: Ive tried the lactation drinks, the lactation brownies and emergency brownies, the lady leche supplement drop and the cookies, peanut butter and salted caramel.Im in love with them all!!! I immediately saw a difference and while my supply has come back I cant stop purchasing theses great products because of the quantity and quality of milk I am getting. Thank you so much Milky Mama!!!

title: It worked
body: I am a low supply mama trying to find anything I could to increase my supply. I was skeptical about the purchase, but after reading reviews, I thought Id give it a shot. They worked! Will he looking into other products I can use daily.

body: This iteM is very tasty

body: I love how the drops help my breasts fill. I am a low producer due to IGT so I can appreciate the extra boost to whatever amounts I can supply to my little one, who is 4 months old now.

author: Sarah M.
title: Maybe helped a little
body: Purchased 2 boxes, eating 2 brownies a day most days, with the hope Id be able to build up a small stash. I did notice a gradual increase but not sure if that was the brownies or because my baby started demanding more. Definitely didnt make enough to put away bags in the freezer. Probably wont buy again as my supply has been unchanged since I ran out but they were truly very tasty.

I take it religiously everyday. Thank you for giving me hope to be able to continue with my breastfeeding journey.

title: It really works!!
body:
These brownies are no joke, let me just say, firstly they taste amazing & secondly they work wonders. Milky Mama's brownies are of good size and keeps full for a long time. I'm an exclusive pumping mama and was producing only 2-3 oz(both sides combined) after having these brownies the next day I saw a difference and produced 4.5 oz (both sides combined). Sometimes i have produced 6 oz too. I try to have only 1 brownie a week so the supply is
constant. I have purchased their cookies too.
I would recommend to all the new mama's out there.

author: renee h.
title: Helping
body: I have been using Lady Leche for 3 weeks now and I can tell a difference in my milk supply.My breast feel fuller and my baby seems more satisfied after a meal. I don't pump so I can't tell if I'm getting more ounces but all signs point to yes! Thank you Milky Mama!

title: Amazing

author: Rachelle T.
title: Tastes AMAZING!!
body: I loved the taste of everything, the drinks were awesome but treats were pretty crumbly though. My supply had dropped from missing a few pumping sessions too early and I was trying a bunch of stuff to get my supply back up. Did these make a significant difference? For me, not really it made my milk milkier but Im not sure if it was these products or a combination of everything I did that got my supply back up. It did take about a week total (the sampler is a 3 day supply if you follow the instructions) to go from 1oz to at least 3oz per breast and I will say these products helped but didnt work a miracle. Id definitely get it again to see if itll give my milk that extra boost since Ive got a better flow and because they taste great.

Day 5 noticed milk increase

author: Courtney W.
title: Boosted supply
body: The brownies definitely helped boost my supply. I recommend this product 100%

author: Katie
title: Ehh
body: I guess I'm in the percentage of women that these products don't work for. I've been using both Pumping Queen and the emergency brownies for almost a week now, and I've seen an increase in my supply by maaaybe two ounces per day, if that. I don't know if the fact that I'm an exclusive pumper getting regular periods is just too much for these products to help with, but they definitely haven't performed the way I hoped or expected - I had significantly better results drinking Mother's Milk tea and doing a power pump, and I think it was the power pump that helped more than anything. Unfortunately, I can no longer power pump because my electric pump died and I've discovered that I actually like my hand pump better. We will continue to supplement with formula, which I'm fine with (fed is best). I was just hoping that Milky Mama would help us save a little in the wallet by increasing my supply, but it hasn't done so. Only giving two stars because I do actually enjoy the taste and texture of the brownies.

author: Darcey M.
title: Lactation brownies
body: Brownies are my absolute favorite , I took these to the hospital with me when I gave birth

author: Shayna W.
title: Delicious
body: Very moist and helpful to my supply, got sick right after I got them and they have helped me keep my supply up!

author: Darcey M.
title: Lemonade packs
body: The lemonades tasted good , not sure if they helped boost my supply because I think the emergency brownies did the trick but good for taste !

author: Darcey M.
title: Emergency brownies
body: The emergency brownies taste so good , they are my go to snack & what makes them even better is that I actually see results with them ! My baby is full after every feeding . I ordered these with my first born but didnt pump on until she was about 3 months . This time around my baby is 1 month and I have over 700 oz frozen !

author: Corine R.
title: Perfect for an exclusive pumper!
body: I love Milk goddess so much. I tried Lady Leche, but I feel like that is more for moms that exclusively feed from the breast. I exclusively pump and I think this is a perfect supplement. On days that I work in the office and forget to use it, I produce less. And on days where I have to miss a pumping session, it helps me produce more to make up for it. I mix it in some fruit punch or my body armor hydration drink and I dont notice any taste.

author: Renee S.
title: Absolutely delish!
body: These are delicious and I definitely see an increase in my milk supply and quality when I eat the recommended 2 per day! Will be buying these again!

author: alina p.
title: High hopes
body: I was sorta of hoping Id see some type of results but nothing changed. I have used over half the bottle in a week and a half as instructed to usage 2x a day. No change in milk supply :(

author: Caitlyn R.
title: No change
body: Im on my second box and so far I have seen no increase. If anything I feel like Im decreasing.. continuing to eat one a day and hoping to at least stay where I am. I have to leave my baby for 2 days which is why I started using them. Been working to have a supply for her when Im gone and Im so disappointed that I dont.

author: Megan P.
title: Great brownies!
body: They were really good and definitely noticed an increase in supply after using! Would recommend!!

author: Sara
title: Worth it
body:
My supply wasnt where it needed to be, so I started pumping in conjunction with trying supplements. I tried Lady Leche and the emergency brownies at the same time. I ate 14 of the brownies and maybe 3 weeks of the Lady Leche. I didnt notice a huge difference.

Then I started taking Lady Leche twice a day, and I definitely noticed a difference in maybe 2-3 days. Before, my breasts always felt empty, and babe used to get so angry around 7-9 at night because I just wasnt making enough. Since I started taking it twice a day, my breasts actually feel full between feeds, my letdown seems faster, and that 7-9 window is no longer a nightmare.

I dont think its made a huge impact on my supply, but taking Lady Leche, in conjunction with pumping and taking moringa, has given me the peace of mind not to worry about making enough milk for my baby. Thats a huge relief. Ill likely purchase again.

The only reason I gave it four stars is the taste. Its not pleasant, but thats something I can easily get passed.

author: Cassandra A.
title: Very very tart/ peely
body: The lemon aid tastes as if the peel was in there. Just very very tart. Dont recommend.

author: Amber
title: No improvement
body: On week 2 of Milky Maiden still havent seen any improvement on supply. Just ordered Lady Leche, going to give it one more shot.

author: Renee S.
title: Absolutely delish!
body: These are delicious and I definitely see an increase in my milk supply and quality when I eat the recommended 2 per day! Will be buying these again!

author: maria V.
title: Love love love.
body: I will continue to buy these everytine I do my milk supply goes up and on top of that theyre DELICIOUS. I eat them everytime Im pumping or feeding!! Love love love!!!

author: Katelyn W.
title: Milk saver.
body: I used this product for only 2 days and I started having 2-3 letdowns in one session!

author: Sarah V.
title: Mini Sampler
body: Cookies and brownies are tasty. I recently experienced a dip in my milk supply due to starting birth control and needed help getting my supply back up. These treats and lady leche supplement (along with lots and lots of water) have helped me! I only wish that I could try ALL the cookie flavors.

author: Shaterra H.
title: Emergency Brownies
body: They didn't help with the increase of my milk supply, but they're very delicious

author: Lynnette W.
title: Forgot it was lactation
body: The cookies was so good I forgot what I was eating them for. My supply increased slightly with the cookies and I would live to see how the drinks work.

author: Martica L.
title: No Title
body: I havnt noticed a difference

author: Violet L.
title: No Title
body: Taste great. Just didnt work for me.

author: Elizabeth D.
title: Delicious
body: I enjoyed these brownies! At first I was skeptical but I gave it some time and I did notice a change in my supply. I went from pumping 4 ounces to 8 eight ounces, sometimes even more. Im starting to have a supply in my freezer which is much needed since Ill be returning to work soon. These brownies are delicious.

author: Yalonda S.
title: Improvement in my "Slacker BooB"
body: After the first use, I noticed that my slacker boob, that only puts out an ounce, put out two and a half ounces. Since then, it has continued to put out two ounces. Also, I have noticed that my milk is creamier.

author: CHARLENE S.
title: It's ok
body: It's OK I haven't noticed a difference at all since I started it and I take it twice a day along with the emergency brownies. Kind if disappointed really.

author: Ann M.
title: Lady leche
body: The product is great for production. The taste is something to get accustomed to if u dont like grape. I have taken this with a brownie everyday and my pumping supply after i feed my baby has doubled in the last 2 weeks.

author: Kassandra L.
title: Tasty treats!
body: My milk supply went from 0.5 oz a pump session to close to 1 oz! The treats are tasty!

author: Amber G.
title: MilkyMama Brownies
body: I bought these for my daughter. They have helped to increase her supply and she says that they taste great! The instructions on storing them was a big help as well. Definitely recommend this product!!

productName: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Lactation Cookies
author: Angelina K.
title: Delicious
body: My milk expression has increased from 2 ounces to about 5 ounces per pump which is great for me because my baby is 8 weeks old and is consuming 2 ounces every 3 hours.

author: Bailee J.
title: Oatmeal cookies
body: The oatmeal cookies are delicious. I freeze all the treats and let them sit out for about 5 mins before eating. The consistency is always good and great flavor.

author: Margaret P.
title: Effective and Delicious
body: I purchased two boxes of the emergency brownies in an effort to raise my low milk supply and reduce the amount of formula I was having to supplement with. Between power pumping and these I noticed an improvement after several days, and have been able to reserve my second box (in the freezer) to use as needed!

author: KRYSTAL A.
title: I cant even...
body: I cant even begin to express how amazing this stuff works for me!

author: Bobbie M.
title: Didnt help with supply issues
body: This did not help my supply issues. It did make my milk creamier which helps my milk go further. I know everyone is different so Its always a gamble.

author: Penelope C.
title: Delicioso!
body: If I could, I would drink it all day!

author: Brittney M.
title: So Good
body: I initially tried these in the sample pack and definitely enjoyed them. These are delicious better than the brownies in my opinion and seemed to help with my supply. I placed another order for these and am currently waiting for them to arrive

author: Samantha H.
title: Works great!
body: Lady Leche works amazingly. My milk production is amped up and my milk is thicker. Also lady Leche tastes surprisingly good, I was expecting that nasty grape medicine taste but it's sweet like a brown sugar sryup with a hint of grape. I would absolutely recommend milky mama products.

author: Delia A.
title: Didnt work for me
body: The taste was good. No after taste. It was sweet and tasty. Unfortunately, I didnt see any results.

author: Nishma R.
title: taste great but didn't help
body: Tasted great but didn't help with supply. I ate 2 one day to help feel engorged and nothing. Same amount that I pump. No increase.

author: Kelsea S.
title: Lactation brownies
body: I was so looking forward to getting these. Unfortunately I have had no luck with the products and my milk supply has gone down drastically :(

author: Kelsea S.
title: Review of product
body: Did not work for me at all Im so sad and I took it faithfully

author: Chaelyn N.
title: Did not work
body: Seemed to be a waste of money for me

productName: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Lactation Cookies
author: Amber W.
title: Perfect snack
body: Love the flavor of this cookie! My go to for a sweet mid day treat with the effects of helping me keep my supply as I have returned back to work.

author: Crystle M.
title: Tasty
body: These brownies were most def delicious but unfortunately they didnt help increase my milk supply at all.

author: Jennifer T.
title: Queen Treatment
body: I bought Pumping Queen and Lady Leche at the same time after my supply decreased as I returned to work. I read that it is recommended to only use one supplement at a time and Pumping Queen was what I decided to start first (2 droppers once a day). It has been a week and I haven't needed to use/start Lady Leche. My supply increased substantially and so did the quality of milk. My baby seems more satisfied after eating. The picture attached is what was pumped this morning AFTER feeding my baby.

author: Jair R.
title: Delicious and Effective
body: I actually look forward to eating these every day!! They're ridiculously delicious. My supply dipped and baby was eating more all at the same time, I ordered some of these, it did take a few days, but then I was back on track.

author: Audrianna L.
title: Incredible
body: Taste was great and my milk supply absolutely improved. I ate them slowly, not once a day, and so naturally they dried out and got a bit harder by the time I finished the box. Thats user error though; these are amazing!

author: Sharlene P.
title: Amazing flavor
body: I love the flavor of the cookies. They tasted really fresh and soft. I did not see any increase in my milk supply though but I am willing to give Milky Mama another try so I ordered the Emergency Brownies. We will see how it goes.

author: Bailee J.
title: Fabulous brownies
body: Love the brownies so much!! Have a hard time only eating one a day!!!

author: Sarah P.
title: Helping (exclusive pumper)
body: I don't want to give all the credit to these because I used these, started power pumping for a few days and started actually pumping on a schedule. I am currently on Lady Leche and drinking 2 galloons of water a day. My supply went from 30 ml from both boobs every few hours to 80-120 ml. I hope it keeps going up! Now I am trying the emergency brownies.

author: Sonja K.
title: Love these!
body: The brownies were delicious and I noticed an increase in my milk supply when using them!

author: Erica D.
title: Great product!
body: I noticed a difference less than 24 hours after using these! My pump output doubled and mu daughter was so full after her morning feed! Will be ordering again

author: Amber G.
title: MilkyMama Emergency Brownies
body: My daughter says that she definitely noticed an increase in her supply during her cycle.

author: Jana D.
title: I Literally cried , HAPPY TEARS!!
body: Where do I begin? How about everything I needed it to do it did and did it QUICK. After 3 days I noticed the first sign that it was working with how much fuller my boobs were and how much faster that they filled. I also noticed my let down was significantly different and way more. After all my baby girl is sleeping better and longer. I was feeling defeated before Lady Leche. Now I cant wait to order some more products.

author: Gabriella A.
title: The best!
body: Ever since starting work, I've noticed a significant decrease in my milk supply. I've been eating 2 emergency brownies everyday with my morning coffee and I've noticed a huge increase in my supply in only a week!! I have enough to feed my baby and then some!! Thank you Milky Mama!!

title: Works great BUT cam cause issues with your babies tummy
body: I absolutely loved it. It did everything that it was supoose to! However, all of a sudden my baby does not tolerate it at all. It makes her constantly poop and ended up with a bad yeast diaper rash due to all of the constantly changes.

author: Christina W.
title: Brownies
body: I can't get past the chalky taste of the brownies. I do like the cookies and drink mix. I have seen a small uptake in lactation

author: Penelope C.
title: Love! Love! Love!

author: Amanda A.

It took 2 days for supply to increase and feedings to become more comfortable. I haven't had anymore issues with mastitis since using the product! I LOVE IT!!

Id say if youve tried other boosters and nothing helps dont bother trying, these will more than likely have the same effect. Some mothers just arent meant to have but a few ounces or just enough and thats OKAY! ?

author: Lianna O.
title: It's okay
body: Taste okay, just didn't work for me.

author: Darial H.L.
title: Lactation brownies
body: Im extremely funny when it comes to textures and tastes but for some odd reason my body could hand it when it came to the brownies the flavor is great and I seen results within two days . The delivery was faster than expected but the product is amazing

author: Stormie
title: AMAZING
body: I would say this is well worth the money great taste and works very well took about to days to work so be patient.

title: Delicious

author: SHERRY C.

body: The products all taste good my fav was the cookies.

author: Kristyn J.
title: Must Have!

body: These brownies are so delicious and has moisture when you bite into them. The texture is perfect with the right amount of chew! Its the right size for a treat thats helping make milk! I appreciate Milky Mama and their products!

author: Kristin M.

title: Awesome
body: It took a little time to get use to the consistency of both the brownie and cookie but I am completely in love with them now!!

author: Heather B.

author: Heather B.

title: Recent purchase
body: I haven't gotten them yet.

title: Yummy in my boobies

author: Latisha T.
title: Didn't increase my supply

author: Heather B.
title: Yummy boobie cookies
body: I love oatmeal cookies, so it makes it even better knowing its helping my supply!

author: Heather B.
title: Emergency no joke!
body: Love these! These definitely work their magic!

author: Heather B.
title: So darn good

author: Leah D.
title: Wasnt right for me
body: Unfortunately, I did not see a change in milk production. That being said this has been a long struggle and not the first product that my body has passed on.

author: Monica F.

title: Melon Madness
body: Taste Ah-mazing! Love the flavor and its so easy to use!

author: Heather B.
title: Milky magic

title: Helps

I know everyone experience will be different just thought this would make a significant difference maybe I need more time or more product which as I have purchased the lactation brownies to help amplify results and process I will not give up just yet and still have faith.

author: Alyssa S.
title: Wonderful and Delicious!
body: Great, I could tell they helped a bit with my milk production!

author: Regina T.
title: Lactation Brownies
body: I think I need more time to have more milk produce. I didnt really notice any difference, but Ill try other products to help.

productName: Peanut Butter Chocolate Chip Lactation Cookies
author: Ruby J.
title: Very delicious
body: So good, buying then again now lol. Im all out!

author: Amber J.
title: My Favorite
body: I love this pack so I'm not eating the same thing every day. These products have doubled my supply and I couldn't be happier!

author: Lisa G.
title: So far so good
body: I like the taste. So far its going well - I have only had a few of them. I would prefer if each packet was a serving, though. Im happy with it!

author: Shianne W.
title: Caused headaches
body: I think my experience with the brownies and the lemonade wouldve been more effective if they didnt make my head hurt. Everytime I ate a brownie or drank the lemonade, my head would ache all day. I was unable to consistently take the brownies and lemonade, so Im not sure if these actually helped my lactation.

author: Roy G.
title: Lady leche and the emergency brownies gave me the boost I needed
body:
Disclaimer : I was previously in a slight oversupply. I usually pumped 5 extra Oz a day on top of what my baby ate. Around the 6 month mark, I had a significant drop in supply, I was not producing enough and had used up almost all of my freezer stash. I was eating double my usual amount , I increased my water intake & I was pumping every 2 hours during the day and twice over night. I was barely producing the 25 Oz that my baby needed & some days I wasnt pumping even that. This product and the emergency brownies gave me the boost I needed !!
I finished the brownies & I am now taking lady leche daily. I just pumped about 11 Oz for my morning pump. I had to take a picture.
I am so thankful for these products!!

author: Brianna R.
title: Like it
body: I like it but I'm having issues with my letdown and I think my body is ready to stop. I also have a hard time pumping often with a toddler and my baby wouldn't latch so I was hoping for more but I think my body is ready to stop.

author: Katelynn S.
title: Really works!
body: As a first time mom of a very hungry little guy, I had a hard time keeping up with him between breastfeeding and pumping. After only a few days of taking this and Lady Leche I went from pumping 2-3 oz to 7-10 oz almost every time (every 4-5 hours)!

author: Kwanza C.
title: Great
body: Ive only ate like 3 of the treats but each time I eat them I feel a difference in my milk.

author: Shanae S.
title: Loving it!!!
body: I dont know what they did this time around but the emergency brownies are much better tasting. I have recently started my menstrual after having my LO whom is now 4 months and realized that everytime I would start my supply would drop. Thanks to the brownies and lady Leche drops I no longer struggle. Baby is happy which means I am happy. They work and they taste amazing.

author: Katelynn S.
title: Really works!

author: Hailey S.
title: Emergency Brownies
body: Overall the brownies are not working so far. Im already almost done with the box and even tried two brownies a day for two days and still nothing. Ive been producing 2-3 oz on one and .5-1.5 oz on the other ranging a total of 3-4 oz a session. I was trying to get ahead so I could have a little extra but still producing the same and hes having to supplement now because he wants around 6 oz a feeding at the moment. The flavor is good and the shipping was fast. I might try something else but not sure yet

author: Abbigail H.
title: Bleh
body: Taste is terrible and it didnt help my supply but again Im under a lot of stress may try again later or try a different product for now didnt help me at all

author: Dexter D.
title: Didn't with
body: They taste good, but did not work to increase milk production at all.

author: Erica V.
title: Great taste
body: I like eating these as a snack but honestly idk if they help my milk supply

author: Katelynn S.
title: Emergency only!
body: These are the real deal! I decided to try one on a whim, and woke up totally engorged! They definitely are for emergencies only lol! But I'm so glad to see they really work! Stocking up to have on hand for when I go back to work!

author: Sharon B.
title: Great deal
body: I purchased the mini sample box. I loved it. The brownies were delicious. The drink powder was great as well. Will definitely be making another purchase. Milky has a new constant customer now.

author: Melanie
title: Yummy and they work!
body:
First of all, they are delicious!
Secondly, they actually work. I noticed this most when I ran out, my production was down.
I do make enough to feed my baby, but barely. At the end of the night, the before bed feed, I run low. And I can't pump any to store without these. But when I snack on one of these daily I need to pump before bed and store 2 bags of milk in the freezer or fridge for later.

Most of all, the worry of "did she get enough?" Goes away..

author: Katelynn S.
title: Really works!
body: As a first time mom of a very hungry little guy, I had a hard time keeping up with him between breastfeeding and pumping. After only a few days of taking this and Dairy Duchess I went from pumping 2-3 oz to 7-10 oz almost every time (every 4-5 hours)!

author: Kristin C.
title: Definitely boosted production!
body: I definitely saw more ounces when I pumped at work.I ate 1/ day for 4 days. Noticing more milk at a day 2. Unfortunately my baby seemed to have an upset tummy while I was using the brownies.

author: Ranie-Ann B.

I recently ordered the emergency brownies since apparently there was none in the sampler, i hope it works or Im going to give up on milky mama. And I did the sampler box with drops as well.

author: Abbigail H.

body: It really didnt help my supply but at the same time Im under a lot of stress so Im unsure I may try again later on when things calm down in life but they did not help me

author: Roy G.
title: I will be buying more !
body: Awesome brownies ! They were tasty and helped me get my supply back up

author: Brieana S.
title: Very good!
body: For now, it seems to be working really well! I had to get use to the taste and flavor, but I am a picky person. The delivery was a lot faster with this one than the emergency brownies, but Im sure its because you all are busy! Thank you for providing these for us moms.

author: Alaina W.
title: No Title
body: Haven't seen any increase

author: Victoria G.
title: No Title
body: They are really good I have not noticed an increase in my milk supply though.

author: Jessica M.
title: No Title
body: The items I purchased are amazing, it has increased my milk supply but not by much. Im not sure if it takes awhile to get at least 4 to 6 oz . On a good day i may get 3 oz .

author: Valeria R.

author: Alora G.

author: Celia G.
